---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import TopNav from '../components/TopNav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Caption from '../components/Caption.astro';
import challongeHeader from '../assets/challonge/Challonge_Header.svg';
import reactLogo from '../assets/challonge/react.svg';
import typescriptLogo from '../assets/challonge/typescript.svg';
import graphqlLogo from '../assets/challonge/graphql.svg';
import storybookLogo from '../assets/challonge/storybook.svg';
import nextjslogo from '../assets/challonge/nextjs.svg';
import discoveryOne from '../assets/challonge/discovery01.png';
import discoveryTwo from '../assets/challonge/discovery02.png';
---

<Layout>
	<TopNav />

	<main class="bg-white" style="font-family: 'TikTok Sans', sans-serif;">
		<section class="relative overflow-hidden border-b border-slate-100 bg-white">
			<!-- Hero gradient band with UI screenshots -->
			<div class="w-full bg-linear-to-r from-emerald-100 via-slate-50 to-rose-100">
				<div class="max-w-[1440px] mx-auto py-8 sm:py-12 lg:py-16 px-4 sm:px-6">
					<!-- Placeholder for hero UI screenshots -->
					<img 
							src={challongeHeader.src} 
							alt="Card-Based Architecture - New job form"
							class="w-full h-auto relative bottom-[-124px]"
						/>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="max-w-[1440px] mx-auto py-8 sm:py-12 lg:py-16 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
			<!-- Title, subtitle, tags -->
			<div class="space-y-4 sm:space-y-6">
				<h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 leading-tight">
					Creating the foundations of a design system on Challonge
				</h1>
				<p class="text-base sm:text-lg lg:text-xl text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
					Providing professional and consistent UI/UX across our platform, while empowering our team to build beautiful and accessible experiences.
				</p>
				<div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2 sm:gap-3">
					<span class="inline-flex items-center px-3 sm:px-4 py-1.5 sm:py-2 rounded-full bg-slate-100 text-slate-700 text-xs sm:text-sm font-medium">B2C SaaS</span>
					<span class="inline-flex items-center px-3 sm:px-4 py-1.5 sm:py-2 rounded-full bg-slate-100 text-slate-700 text-xs sm:text-sm font-medium">Design System</span>
					<span class="inline-flex items-center px-3 sm:px-4 py-1.5 sm:py-2 rounded-full bg-slate-100 text-slate-700 text-xs sm:text-sm font-medium">Project Management</span>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- About -->
			<div class="mt-8 sm:mt-10 space-y-3 sm:space-y-4">
				<h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900">About</h2>
				<p class="text-base sm:text-lg lg:text-xl text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
					This project focused on building a comprehensive design system for Challonge, a tournament management platform, to improve UI/UX consistency and empower the team to create consistent and reusable experiences. The design system serves as the foundation for maintaining a unified look and feel across the platform while streamlining design and development workflows.
				</p>
			</div>

			<!-- Team -->
			<div class="mt-8 sm:mt-10 space-y-3 sm:space-y-4">
				<h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900">Team</h2>
				<ul class="space-y-2 sm:space-y-3 text-base sm:text-lg lg:text-xl text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
					<li class="flex items-start gap-2 sm:gap-3">
						<span class="text-indigo-400 text-lg sm:text-xl mt-1 shrink-0"><i class="ri-user-line"></i></span>
						<span>1 Product Designer</span>
					</li>
					<li class="flex items-start gap-2 sm:gap-3">
						<span class="text-indigo-400 text-lg sm:text-xl mt-1 shrink-0"><i class="ri-user-line"></i></span>
						<span>6 software developers, 1 QA, 1 tech lead, 2 product owners</span>
					</li>
				</ul>
			</div>

			<!-- Goals -->
			<div class="mt-8 sm:mt-10 space-y-6 sm:space-y-8">
				<h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900">Goals</h2>
				
				<!-- Design Goals -->
				<div class="space-y-4 sm:space-y-6">
					<h3 class="text-lg sm:text-2xl lg:text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">Design Goals</h3>
					<div class="grid gap-4 sm:gap-6 lg:grid-cols-2">
						<div class="p-4 sm:p-6 rounded-xl bg-blue-50 border border-blue-100 space-y-3 sm:space-y-4">
							<div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
								<span class="text-2xl text-indigo-600"><i class="ri-palette-line"></i></span>
								<h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">1. Consistency</h3>
							</div>
							<p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
								Ensuring a unified look and feel across the entire Challonge platform, creating a cohesive user experience that reflects our brand identity and design principles.
							</p>
						</div>
						<div class="p-4 sm:p-6 rounded-xl bg-blue-50 border border-blue-100 space-y-3 sm:space-y-4">
							<div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
								<span class="text-2xl text-indigo-600"><i class="ri-speed-up-line"></i></span>
								<h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">2. Efficiency</h3>
							</div>
							<p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
								Streamlining design and development workflows by providing reusable components and clear guidelines, reducing time spent on repetitive tasks and decision-making.
							</p>
						</div>
						<div class="p-4 sm:p-6 rounded-xl bg-blue-50 border border-blue-100 space-y-3 sm:space-y-4">
							<div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
								<span class="text-2xl text-indigo-600"><i class="ri-expand-left-right-line"></i></span>
								<h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">3. Scalability</h3>
							</div>
							<p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
								Supporting future growth and new features by establishing a flexible and extensible design system that can adapt to evolving product needs.
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- Business Goals -->
				<div class="space-y-4 sm:space-y-6">
					<h3 class="text-lg sm:text-2xl lg:text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">Business Goals</h3>
					<div class="grid gap-4 sm:gap-6 lg:grid-cols-2">
						<div class="p-4 sm:p-6 rounded-xl bg-blue-50 border border-blue-100 space-y-3 sm:space-y-4">
							<div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
								<span class="text-2xl text-indigo-600"><i class="ri-rocket-line"></i></span>
								<h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">1. Increased productivity and faster iteration</h3>
							</div>
							<p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
								Allows the team to deliver projects faster and allocate resources more effectively.
							</p>
						</div>
						<div class="p-4 sm:p-6 rounded-xl bg-blue-50 border border-blue-100 space-y-3 sm:space-y-4">
							<div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
								<span class="text-2xl text-indigo-600"><i class="ri-user-heart-line"></i></span>
								<h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">2. Enhanced UX</h3>
							</div>
							<p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
								Allows for the creation of user-friendly, intuitive interfaces that can lead to higher user engagement, retention, and satisfaction.
							</p>
						</div>
						<div class="p-4 sm:p-6 rounded-xl bg-blue-50 border border-blue-100 space-y-3 sm:space-y-4">
							<div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
								<span class="text-2xl text-indigo-600"><i class="ri-line-chart-line"></i></span>
								<h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">3. Scalability</h3>
							</div>
							<p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
								Ensures that the user experience remains consistent and high-quality, even as the organization introduces new products or services.
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- Constraints -->
			<div class="mt-8 sm:mt-10 space-y-4 sm:space-y-6">
				<h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900">Constraints</h2>
				<div class="grid gap-4 sm:gap-6 lg:grid-cols-2">
					<div class="p-4 sm:p-6 rounded-xl bg-amber-50 border border-amber-100 space-y-3 sm:space-y-4">
						<div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
							<span class="text-2xl text-amber-600"><i class="ri-moon-line"></i></span>
							<h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">1. Dark UI</h3>
						</div>
						<p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
							The design system should primarily focus on dark theme but could still be open to scale for other themes in the future.
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="p-4 sm:p-6 rounded-xl bg-amber-50 border border-amber-100 space-y-3 sm:space-y-4">
						<div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
							<span class="text-2xl text-amber-600"><i class="ri-user-star-line"></i></span>
							<h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">2. Overlord Governance</h3>
						</div>
						<p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
							As the sole lead designer for the team, I am responsible for the decisions that are related to the design system.
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="p-4 sm:p-6 rounded-xl bg-amber-50 border border-amber-100 space-y-3 sm:space-y-4">
						<div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
							<span class="text-2xl text-amber-600"><i class="ri-layout-grid-line"></i></span>
							<h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">3. Foundational Styles and Components</h3>
						</div>
						<p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
							Only scoped to foundational styles and components. These include colors, typography, and widely used components like form elements, cards, tables, etc.
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="p-4 sm:p-6 rounded-xl bg-amber-50 border border-amber-100 space-y-3 sm:space-y-4">
						<div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
							<span class="text-2xl text-amber-600"><i class="ri-file-text-line"></i></span>
							<h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">4. Minimal Documentation</h3>
						</div>
						<p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
							Focused our energy on building the components visually then refine the documentation and guidelines after.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- Technology -->
			<div class="mt-8 sm:mt-10 space-y-4 sm:space-y-6">
				<h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900">Technology</h2>
				<div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-6 sm:gap-8">
					<div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-2">
						<div class="w-16 h-16 sm:w-20 sm:h-20 flex items-center justify-center">
							<span class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl">
								<img src={reactLogo.src} alt="React" class="w-full h-full" />
							</span>
						</div>
						<span class="text-sm sm:text-base text-slate-700 font-medium">React</span>
					</div>
					<div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-2">
						<div class="w-16 h-16 sm:w-20 sm:h-20 flex items-center justify-center">
							<span class="text-sm sm:text-base font-bold text-blue-600"><img src={typescriptLogo.src} alt="TypeScript" class="w-full h-full" /></span>
						</div>
						<span class="text-sm sm:text-base text-slate-700 font-medium">TypeScript</span>
					</div>
					<div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-2">
						<div class="w-16 h-16 sm:w-20 sm:h-20 flex items-center justify-center">
							<span class="text-xl sm:text-2xl"><img src={graphqlLogo.src} alt="GraphQL" class="w-full h-full" /></span>
						</div>
						<span class="text-sm sm:text-base text-slate-700 font-medium">GraphQL</span>
					</div>
					<div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-2">
						<div class="w-16 h-16 sm:w-20 sm:h-20 flex items-center justify-center">
							<span class="text-sm sm:text-base font-bold text-pink-600"><img src={storybookLogo.src} alt="Storybook" class="w-full h-full" /></span>
						</div>
						<span class="text-sm sm:text-base text-slate-700 font-medium">Storybook</span>
					</div>
					<div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-2">
						<div class="w-16 h-16 sm:w-20 sm:h-20 flex items-center justify-center">
							<span class="text-sm sm:text-base font-bold text-pink-600"><img src={nextjslogo.src} alt="Next.js" class="w-full h-full" /></span>
						</div>
						<span class="text-sm sm:text-base text-slate-700 font-medium">NextJS</span>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- Discovery -->
			<div class="mt-8 sm:mt-10 space-y-4 sm:space-y-6">
				<h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900">Discovery</h2>
				<p class="text-base sm:text-lg lg:text-xl text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
					The feature started through one of the best methods to gather feedback from ours users: using our own product and actually organizing our own Tekken 7 tournament!
				</p>
				
				<!-- Two images side-by-side -->
				<div class="grid gap-4 sm:gap-6 lg:grid-cols-2">
					<div class="flex flex-col gap-3 sm:gap-4">
						<div class="rounded-4xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 overflow-hidden flex items-center justify-center">
							<img src={discoveryOne.src} alt="Challonge Tournament" class="w-full h-full" />
						</div>
						<Caption text="Me and the CTO checking-in participants." />
					</div>
					<div class="flex flex-col gap-3 sm:gap-4">
						<div class="rounded-4xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 overflow-hidden flex items-center justify-center">
							<img src={discoveryTwo.src} alt="Challonge Tournament" class="w-full h-full" />
						</div>
						<Caption text="Challonge to Major tournament bracket in action." />
					</div>
				</div>
				
				<!-- Feedback Section -->
				<div class="grid gap-4 sm:gap-6 lg:grid-cols-2 mt-6">
					<div class="p-4 sm:p-6 rounded-xl bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200">
						<p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-slate-600 mb-2">Feedback by lead product manager</p>
						<p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
							The design system will be crucial for maintaining consistency as we scale. We need to ensure it's flexible enough to accommodate future features while maintaining our brand identity.
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="p-4 sm:p-6 rounded-xl bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200">
						<div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
							<div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-slate-300"></div>
							<div>
								<p class="text-sm sm:text-base font-semibold text-slate-900">Mark J.</p>
								<p class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-slate-600">Product Manager</p>
							</div>
						</div>
						<p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
							This initiative will significantly improve our development velocity and design consistency across the platform.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- User Interviews & Surveys -->
				<div class="mt-6">
					<h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 sm:mb-6">User Interviews & Surveys</h3>
					<div class="grid gap-4 sm:gap-6 lg:grid-cols-3">
						<div class="p-4 sm:p-6 rounded-xl bg-indigo-50 border border-indigo-100">
							<div class="text-3xl text-indigo-600 mb-3">
								<i class="ri-user-line"></i>
							</div>
							<h4 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">User Pain Points</h4>
							<p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
								Identified key usability issues and areas where the current UI/UX falls short of user expectations.
							</p>
						</div>
						<div class="p-4 sm:p-6 rounded-xl bg-indigo-50 border border-indigo-100">
							<div class="text-3xl text-indigo-600 mb-3">
								<i class="ri-search-line"></i>
							</div>
							<h4 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Feature Requests</h4>
							<p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
								Collected and analyzed user requests for new features and improvements to existing functionality.
							</p>
						</div>
						<div class="p-4 sm:p-6 rounded-xl bg-indigo-50 border border-indigo-100">
							<div class="text-3xl text-indigo-600 mb-3">
								<i class="ri-focus-3-line"></i>
							</div>
							<h4 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">User Goals</h4>
							<p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
								Understood primary user objectives and how the design system can better support their workflows.
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- Competitive Analysis -->
				<div class="mt-6">
					<h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 sm:mb-4">Competitive Analysis</h3>
					<p class="text-base sm:text-lg lg:text-xl text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
						We analyzed competitor platforms to understand industry standards, identify best practices, and find opportunities for differentiation. This research helped inform our design decisions and ensure we're building a design system that meets modern user expectations.
					</p>
					<div class="flex flex-col gap-3 sm:gap-4">
						<div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 overflow-hidden aspect-video flex items-center justify-center">
							<span class="text-slate-500 text-sm">Competitive Analysis UI Grid Placeholder</span>
						</div>
						<Caption text="Competitive analysis of design patterns and UI components." />
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- Design -->
			<div class="mt-8 sm:mt-10 space-y-4 sm:space-y-6">
				<h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900">Design</h2>
				<p class="text-base sm:text-lg lg:text-xl text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
					The design process focused on creating a cohesive visual language and a comprehensive component library. We established design tokens, defined typography scales, color systems, and spacing guidelines that would serve as the foundation for all UI components.
				</p>

				<!-- Visual Language -->
				<div class="mt-6">
					<h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 sm:mb-6">Visual Language</h3>
					<div class="grid gap-4 sm:gap-6 lg:grid-cols-3">
						<div class="p-4 sm:p-6 rounded-xl bg-purple-50 border border-purple-100">
							<div class="text-3xl text-purple-600 mb-3">
								<i class="ri-palette-line"></i>
							</div>
							<h4 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Color Palette</h4>
							<p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
								Established a comprehensive color system with primary, secondary, and semantic colors that support both light and dark themes.
							</p>
						</div>
						<div class="p-4 sm:p-6 rounded-xl bg-purple-50 border border-purple-100">
							<div class="text-3xl text-purple-600 mb-3">
								<i class="ri-font-size-2"></i>
							</div>
							<h4 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Typography</h4>
							<p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
								Defined a typographic scale with clear hierarchy, ensuring readability and consistency across all text elements.
							</p>
						</div>
						<div class="p-4 sm:p-6 rounded-xl bg-purple-50 border border-purple-100">
							<div class="text-3xl text-purple-600 mb-3">
								<i class="ri-layout-grid-line"></i>
							</div>
							<h4 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Layout & Spacing</h4>
							<p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
								Created a consistent spacing system and layout guidelines that ensure visual harmony and proper content organization.
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- Component Library -->
				<div class="mt-6">
					<h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 sm:mb-4">Component Library</h3>
					<p class="text-base sm:text-lg lg:text-xl text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
						We developed a comprehensive library of reusable UI components, each designed with accessibility, consistency, and flexibility in mind. Components were built to work seamlessly together while maintaining their individual functionality.
					</p>
					<div class="flex flex-col gap-3 sm:gap-4">
						<div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 overflow-hidden aspect-video flex items-center justify-center">
							<span class="text-slate-500 text-sm">Component Library Dashboard Placeholder</span>
						</div>
						<Caption text="Component library dashboard showcasing reusable UI components." />
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- Design System Documentation -->
				<div class="mt-6">
					<h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 sm:mb-4">Design System Documentation</h3>
					<p class="text-base sm:text-lg lg:text-xl text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
						Comprehensive documentation was created to ensure the design system is easily accessible and understandable for all team members. This includes usage guidelines, code examples, design specifications, and best practices for each component.
					</p>
					<div class="flex flex-col gap-3 sm:gap-4">
						<div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 overflow-hidden aspect-video flex items-center justify-center">
							<span class="text-slate-500 text-sm">Design System Documentation Placeholder</span>
						</div>
						<Caption text="Design system documentation interface showing component specifications and guidelines." />
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- Showcase -->
			<div class="mt-8 sm:mt-10 space-y-4 sm:space-y-6">
				<h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900">Showcase</h2>
				<p class="text-base sm:text-lg lg:text-xl text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
					The design system in action across various screens and components, demonstrating how the unified design language creates a cohesive and professional user experience throughout the Challonge platform.
				</p>

				<!-- UI Screenshots Grid -->
